survey_response.review_text:
Dr. Jyoti is very professional and efficient in her work. The first step of getting a dental implant consists of drilling into the jaw bone and securing a nail there, which is left for two months for absolute healing. Dr. Jyoti made this entire scary sounding procedure almost painless. Her clinic is one stop solution for all dental problems. Doctors and staff are well versed with their work and have all advanced machineries to carry out complicated procedures. Their behavior and explanation of the procedure is excellent.

I would recommend 'Cosmodent'  and Dr. Jyoti as well as Dr. Anand Narla (for braces) to all in need of a dental problem.

Very satisfied , highly recommend 
Please once for experience. All the best to the team.
............

Dr. Jyoti Narla is a very patient and knowledgable doctor in her field. 
She gave me the right advice on way forward and recommended the best remedy anyone could be happpy with. 

She also helped in getting the apppointment the next day for the wisdom tooth removal since mine was half broken. She explained the whole procedure to me and told me not to fret on it since all shall go well. 

She is friendly and being an expert in her field, am very happy with the time she spent answering my queries and being friendly. I highly recommend her for toooth related problem. Along with her competent team, it was a satisfying and seamless experience.

review_reply.reply_text: Thanks for your kind words & appreciation

survey_response.review_text: She is a very good n great Doctor.  Her approach towards patients was very sweet.  Her treatment was not giving any pain or uncomfort after the treatment.  Overall she is a very very good 👍 and fantastic fabulous 👌🏼  Doctor.  Her staffs are also very nice n approach towards patients was sweet

Dr. Jyoti and Dr. Anand have been my dentists for almost a decade now. Given my persistent teeth issue (which also led to bad breath and extreme sensitivity) I had consulted multiple dentists in the past. It was Dr Jothi and Dr. Anand  @ Cosmodent Clinic (Chandivali, Powai) that explained the root cause (Deep Bite condition) and recommended  appropriate solution. They simplified my trauma to a great degree, and so I am forever thankful to them. Dr. Jyoti is a Gum Surgen, and Dr Anand an Orthodontic Specialist. Both are thorough professionals in their respective spaces. They will be my dentists forever.

Well experienced professional, extremely comforting
Explained well in detail.

Focus was on resolving the issue instead of a short term solution. 

Her understanding was very good. And she focused on what is right for the patient. 

Impressed with the Machines / equipments. Clarity of teeth images, X-ray etc etc. Didn’t find such detailing thru equipments at an another dentist.


She is v v good. Went to her after visiting few other dentists and was Super Delighted.

Highly recommended

** ***** ** *** ***** I had crown fell off from the root canal. Tooth involved in root canal was decayed and few Dentists suggested me for implant but Dr Jyoti and Keni recommended to save the original tooth. She did the necessary treatment of post and core and I am one happy soul once again. Dr Keni who did the initial check up and did the crown work is also very talented and very good in explaining the course of treatment.
Dr Jyoti is excellent in what she does. Highly recommended. Staff is very polite,  professional and cooperative. The clinic is very clean ,hygienic and well equipped with all hi-tech equipments. I found my dentist for a life now 👍

review_reply.reply_text: Thanks a ton for your kind words... Hope to see you soon for follow up

survey_response.review_text:
I have been undergoing treatment from Dr Jyoti for over six months - from basic filling, root canal, wisdom teeth extractions, implants etc * * ***** **** ** *** **** ***** ********* *** **** ********

Dr. Jyoti is a Doctor gifted with the "Healing Touch" - she is, by nature, very sensitive, aware of the patient's discomfort / fears and with her professional competence, she ensures that the treatment is without pain *** *******.  She is one of the rare Doctors who respects the patient's time ,manages her time well and ensures that appointments are as per schedule.

In summary, Dr Jyoti is an awesome Doctor in all respects and I would strongly recommend her without hesitation. And like many others have said, if you have fears of dental treatments, these will vanish, for sure !!

survey_response.review_text: Dr Jyoti provides one of the most painless and friendly treatment. She's so patient.... And understanding. Myself and my two daughters got cavity fillings done from her and I can vouch for it that we never had such a comfortable dental treatment ever.My younger baby is no more scared of fillings.... With a TV in front of her eyes, small gifts given on every visit and best thing the very friendly nature of Dr.... The beautiful interiors... Dentist visit is no more a scary thing for our family... Thanks to the lovely Dr and her team!

I visited Dr Jyoti for the first time for a painful cavity in my molar tooth. I was postponing my visit to a dentist dreading the pain of rootcanal. Dr Jyoti carefully examined my teeth and suggested that the cavity just be filled right now and rootcanal can wait. I really appreciate her honest approach. Now the dental treatment starts. * **** *** **** *** ** *** **** ******* ** *** *** **** * **** ********** ******** She understands the concerns, explains do's and don'ts and has the most advanced technologies for a pain free dental experience. I am very happy with her treatments. Her clinic is also spot clean and staff and ambience is very welcoming. I think I have found the dentist I was looking for who does minimal damage to my teeth and pocket! Thank you Dr Jyoti. I highly recommend her for any dental work related to teeth, gums and dental health.

review_reply.reply_text:
Follow up visit - tooth Enamel gets chipped  
Ans:It's not the tooth we treated 

Charged additional 500
Ans :500 for 2 X rays for new problem  of Enamel chipping and related sensitivity

Food lodgement problem

Cost

All we say is if u do complain and it isn't sorted then u should be upset 

We feel sorry for ur inconvenience 
Please come back to us and help us to serve u better

survey_response.review_text: Super expensive but quality of treatment below average. I went to treat a lot of cavities. The Doc ended up replacing a bridge, and the new one has a huge gap where food keeps getting stuck. The cavities that were filled has left the teeth a little misaligned. Also, one tooth enamel got chipped off within a few days and when I went back to get it fixed, she just recommended a sensitivity toothpaste that doesn't work and even charged 500 for it. Overall I spent about 40,000 Rs on the treatment and totally regret it. There are way better dentists around if you want to spend that much.

I had heard terrible stories of root canal - the tediousness, the pain; the headache etc. Naturally my first root canal and I was anxious and nervous to the point had rescheduled my appointment twice. When I finally got on that chair under the lights,I was nervous and anticipated the pain I had heard so much about being associated with this treatment. But the providence of God in Dr Jyoti, who was brilliant and adept in treating it- I had no pain even post the treatment last night, coz she advised me to have the pain killer before the anaesthesia wears off, I am going in to get the cap set . Dr. Jyoti with her professional touch and efficiency, totally settled my anxiety about this treatment and now I have a testimony different from the ones have heard. Am so grateful. I would definitely recommend Dr Jyoti at Cosmodent and the patience she has 🙏🏼With answering whatever questions I had out of anxiety. Thank you

I had taken my dad earlier (91yrs) to Dr Jyoti for a tooth filling...just 2-3 months later the filling came out....i was upset I had to take him again as it's  very difficult task considering his age...however when I met Dr Jyoti she clearly explained to me that it was not the filling but that a small piece of the tooth had chipped off creating the hole..i was not very convinced but seeing that i was not happy with the situation..she offered to fill up the hole and did not charge me for it either!! It was a very kind gesture and I felt glad I had gone back to her...she is very understanding of a situation...she does her job in a very calm and patient manner and my dad too is quite relaxed during these sessions which is wonderful! I strongly recommend Dr Jyoti and assure you that you will not be disappointed. Thank you Dr Jyoti for being, not just a Dr but also a good human being.

review_reply.reply_text:
You have taken your daughter's appointment for a deep cavity  & on examination it was noticed that there were multiple cavities in front, back teeth on both side & she had complaints of frequent food lodgement in wisdom teeth. In order to check the extent of depth of cavities & condition of wisdom teeth we would require a full mouth xray without the x ray we can't tell the treatment plan.

Even though you didn't take any prior appointment for your checkup of severe toothache & sensitivity still we accomodated you which after the examination revealed that you need a root canal treatment which would require time. 

For proper treatment need good examination & diagnosis which is not possible without x-rays. You both didn't have any old records also.

We charged for consultation & full mouth single x rays taken separately for both of you. Treatment plan was explained in detail & prescription also was given. For further treatment asked to take appointment as the next patient was also waiting in the reception.

survey_response.review_text:
Guys.. Please read this if you want a genuine feedback!!
When I shifted in Mumbai and had some dental problems, I went to Cosmodent without any references. Even during my first visit, Jyoti Mam was able to gauge the exact difficulties which I was facing in front teeth. With the kind of friendliness ever thought of, she handled all steps of such dental surgeries very carefully and promptly. The exact treatment what you want with the timelines guided was provided. And the same continues even today. She remembers which tooth surgery was done earlier. And with the same treatment appropriateness, she handled all carefully in the required manner. Hats Off!! I owe to you a lot!! My family or my friends will come to Cosmodent Powai for any dental treatments, wherever we all live in Mumbai.

It was an incredible experience with Doctor Jyoti. I went with my 8 year old son Vivaan for dental examination. He was very scared as this was his first visit. Not only did Dr. Jyoti made us comfortable, she also gave us space and time to decide on our next course of action. 

We know that final answer to my son’s issue may be tooth extraction but getting that comfort to decide how and when was a big relief.

I am now spending time assuring my son that we must get it done and we will, we know that Dr. Jyoti is there to take care of things and guide us well.

Thank you Doctor and God Bless!

Cheers

Hitesh

****** ******* *** with a courteous demeanour. Had been there for RCT, Crown fixing and Filling. While for same task in totality, other Dentists in and around Powai had quoted 75-85K, I got my treatment done at 42k at Cosmodent. The clinic is ultra modern and spanky clean. Team of professional staff. What impressed me the most is the time Dr. Narla devoted and was never in a hurry to ensure that entire experience is painless and to perfection. 
I would strongly recommend Cosmodent to all seeking dental treatment. Don’t go by the sky rocketing obnoxious prices that are quoted by other Dr’s/Hospitals and get a check done at this clinic. You won’t repent my suggestion out of my experience.
